                                                                                                                <comments>
                            <comment id="15839704" author="gurwls223" created="Thu, 26 Jan 2017 13:57:09 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Can we just strip them within the dataframe/dataset? Available options for read/write are well documented. IMHO, we should not just add options/APIs just for consistency.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="15889117" author="gurwls223" created="Tue, 28 Feb 2017 23:33:59 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Oh, I overlooked. You meant it always strips the white spaces when writing out via CSV datasource?&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="15889120" author="abridgett" created="Tue, 28 Feb 2017 23:36:37 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Yep, that&apos;s right. Sorry - not sure why I didn&apos;t reply to your initial comment!&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="15923338" author="tenstriker" created="Tue, 14 Mar 2017 00:51:23 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;I am having same issue. Created &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/SPARK-19942&quot; title=&quot;DataFrameWriter - CSV options &amp;quot;ignoreLeadingWhiteSpace&amp;quot; and &amp;quot;ignoreTrailingWhiteSpace&amp;quot; Not working&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;SPARK-19942&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;SPARK-19942&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt;. It seems like this was a issue in spark-csv module as well and they fixed it but not sure it got ported in spark module.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="15923343" author="gurwls223" created="Tue, 14 Mar 2017 00:56:14 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;It is not implemented in spark-csv library (see &lt;a href=&quot;https://github.com/databricks/spark-csv/pull/306&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://github.com/databricks/spark-csv/pull/306&lt;/a&gt;) I raised this PR but at that time CSV datasource was ported into Spark. So, I decided to close that.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;For CSV datasource in Spark, I think it is worth checking it. I will check this when I have some time.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;BTW, let me close  &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/SPARK-19942&quot; title=&quot;DataFrameWriter - CSV options &amp;quot;ignoreLeadingWhiteSpace&amp;quot; and &amp;quot;ignoreTrailingWhiteSpace&amp;quot; Not working&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;SPARK-19942&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;SPARK-19942&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt; as a duplicate as you said.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="15928065" author="gurwls223" created="Thu, 16 Mar 2017 13:54:19 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;I submitted a PR for this &lt;a href=&quot;https://github.com/apache/spark/pull/17310&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://github.com/apache/spark/pull/17310&lt;/a&gt; but it seems not adding a link automatically for now.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="15931567" author="apachespark" created="Sun, 19 Mar 2017 04:49:02 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;User &apos;HyukjinKwon&apos; has created a pull request for this issue:&lt;br/&gt;
